title: Lowest international tourism receipts for passenger transport
description: In 2019, Guinea-Bissau had one of the lowest international tourism receipts for passenger transport, amounting to just $20,000.

title: Highest food imports as a percentage of merchandise imports
description: In 2018, food imports constituted 41.71% of Guinea-Bissau's merchandise imports, one of the highest percentages globally.

title: Lowest manufactures exports as a percentage of merchandise exports
description: In 2015, manufactures exports made up only 0.00009% of Guinea-Bissau's merchandise exports, one of the lowest proportions worldwide.
